    "description": "Tandem is a scientific software for SEAS modelling and for solving\nPoisson and linear elasticity problems. It implements the Symmetric\nInterior Penalty Galerkin (SIPG) method using unstructured simplicial\nmeshes (triangle meshes in 2D, tetrahedral meshes in 3D).\n",
